title: Von Miller Interview, Jason La Canfora on Week 2 Overreactions (Football 09/19)
description:
Will Brinson is joined by CBS Sports NFL Insider Jason La Canfora to break down the biggest overreactions from Week 2 of the NFL season, including whether or not the Steelers are in trouble, if Ryan Fitzpatrick can keep his job and if Blake Bortles is ascending into the upper echelon of NFL quarterbacks. Will also breaks down the biggest NFL news and is joined by Broncos superstar pass rusher Von Miller to talk about the team's 2-0 start.
